{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"antelopine-airworthy-quokka","description":"## Context\nFoundational encoder for every rebar signature: the DSSE v1.0.0 envelope and Pre-Authentication Encoding so signatures cover exact opaque bytes and never a re-serialized JSON form. Everything else in the foundation builds on this.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] `src/rebar/attest/dsse.py` implements `pae(payload_type, body)->bytes` per spec (\"DSSEv1\" SP len(type) SP type SP len(body) SP body) plus envelope `{payload,payloadType,signatures:[{keyid,sig}]}` encode/decode.\n- [ ] Unit test verifies PAE against the DSSE spec's worked example (byte-exact).\n- [ ] Unit test with duplicate/re-ordered JSON keys shows verify operates on the exact stored bytes (no re-serialization).","id":"9fd5-0074-a995-43e6","parent_id":"2fd4-baa0-4471-4382","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"attest: DSSE envelope + PAE encoder/decoder"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783735837400834001,"uuid":"ae44558b-27e6-4186-a7dc-8d6afbf9d62c"}